'legacy_l_154','legacy_u_17','Copper Top Street Light',NULL,'A single classic Victorian style street light salvaged from the City of London, Westminster. An attractively shaped copper top featuring its original plastic screen, this has been rewired (for display purposes) and mounted on a bespoke steel stand. A fantastic feature for a driveway, garden, patio, Yard... Get in touch to discuss national delivery or flexible collection. Height / 225cm Diameter of base / 60cm',38000,'used',(SELECT "id" FROM "Category" WHERE "slug" = 'hardware-fixtures' LIMIT 1),NULL,NULL,NULL,ARRAY['https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202108/img_1920x_610933ff7fff85-68903251-20112034.jpg']::text[],'active','sell','LOT',NULL,false,NULL,NULL,true,'2021-08-03T12:18:05Z'::timestamptz,'2021-08-03T12:18:05Z'::timestamptz);

