'legacy_l_155','legacy_u_17','Pair of Salvaged London Street Lights',NULL,'A pair of Victorian style street lights salvaged from the City of London (Westminster). Featuring their original plastic screens, these have been rewired (for display purposes) and mounted on bespoke collars on to steel stands. A fantastic feature for a driveway, garden, patio, Yard... Get in touch to discuss national delivery or flexible collection. Height / 250cm Diameter of base / 70cm',84000,'used',(SELECT "id" FROM "Category" WHERE "slug" = 'hardware-fixtures' LIMIT 1),NULL,NULL,NULL,ARRAY['https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202108/img_1920x_610934034db516-61824153-39917662.jpg']::text[],'active','sell','LOT',NULL,false,NULL,NULL,true,'2021-08-03T12:18:09Z'::timestamptz,'2021-08-03T12:18:09Z'::timestamptz);

