'legacy_l_159','legacy_u_17','Cast Iron Lamp Post',NULL,'Around 365cm tall, this salvaged cast iron lamp post is a superb example of Victorian manufacture. The top of the light rests into the main body. I would reccomend that a new plug or stopper is sourced. I have simply used some wedges made from wood.Fixed to a 25cm square plinth. Very easily wired and very heavy.',38000,'used',(SELECT "id" FROM "Category" WHERE "slug" = 'hardware-fixtures' LIMIT 1),NULL,NULL,NULL,ARRAY['https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202108/img_1920x_6109340ee74fe4-53109364-52374767.jpg']::text[],'active','sell','LOT',NULL,false,NULL,NULL,true,'2021-08-03T12:18:22Z'::timestamptz,'2021-08-03T12:18:22Z'::timestamptz);

