'legacy_l_264','legacy_u_17','Minos Cretan Terracotta Jar',NULL,'Named after a famous King of Crete, the Minos Cretan terracotta jar is a beautiful decoraitve vessel based on an ancient Cretan artifact. Traditionally made from the finest Cretan clay and spun on a potters wheel. Get in touch to discuss national delivery or flexible collection. Cretan Terracotta Frost-Resistant Hand-Thrown Amazing colour Plants LOVE them Height / 35cm Width / 25cm',4500,'used',(SELECT "id" FROM "Category" WHERE "slug" = 'other' LIMIT 1),NULL,NULL,NULL,ARRAY['https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202108/img_1920x_61094d77bb6660-25859133-86936576.jpg']::text[],'active','sell','LOT',NULL,false,NULL,NULL,true,'2021-08-03T14:06:46Z'::timestamptz,'2021-08-03T14:06:46Z'::timestamptz);

