'legacy_l_324','legacy_u_8','Under and Over roof tiles',NULL,'Thes clay tiles are ideal for a garden room project as they can be fitted at a low pitch. I am looking to get rid of them as a lot and have about 4 pallets of them, am ususure of the exact number. Great for a roof covering but would also work well for use in a water faeature etc. Tiles are available to view any time during working hours, Price depicted is based upon collection. owever, we would be happy to ship at an additional cost.',15000,'used',(SELECT "id" FROM "Category" WHERE "slug" = 'roof-tiles-slates' LIMIT 1),NULL,NULL,NULL,ARRAY['https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202108/img_1920x_610d03a2e2a888-67302065-44899122.jpeg','https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202108/img_1920x_610d03aaad3f75-14833688-33478495.jpeg']::text[],'active','sell','LOT',NULL,false,NULL,NULL,true,'2021-08-06T09:52:32Z'::timestamptz,'2021-08-06T09:52:32Z'::timestamptz);

