'legacy_l_341','legacy_u_3','Mini Stack | Designer wood burner ex display | 25% off RRP',NULL,'An ex display Mini Stack in Bliue and white on wooden legs. The Mini stack is a superb little wood burning stove that will make a great focal point in any room. The stove has been in our showroom for about a year but it is now time to let her go. At Hot Box, we can supply and install this stove to your exact requiremetns so please message us for more info or visit us online to make contact. Alternatively, check out online here to get a great deal on this ex display wood burning stove.',500000,'used',(SELECT "id" FROM "Category" WHERE "slug" = 'other' LIMIT 1),NULL,0,0,ARRAY['https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202109/img_1920x_6137317b37a845-57895678-22008603.jpeg','https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202109/img_1920x_613731a21da411-13650719-15245657.jpeg','https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202109/img_1920x_6137319cb120c7-39738578-11582880.jpeg','https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202109/img_1920x_6137319727e109-12039750-54624875.jpeg','https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202109/img_1920x_61373191929420-40364272-20545672.jpeg','https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202109/img_1920x_6137318bf0a350-06463664-37281020.jpeg','https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202109/img_1920x_6137318649c6a2-63522753-68029113.jpeg','https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202109/img_1920x_61373180cd72e4-91612023-40068952.jpeg']::text[],'active','sell','LOT',NULL,true,100,NULL,true,'2021-09-07T09:34:41Z'::timestamptz,'2021-09-07T09:34:41Z'::timestamptz);

