'legacy_l_396','legacy_u_68','5 Pack of Reclaimed Sandtoft Old English Pantiles Natural Clay Colour',NULL,'5 Pack of Reclaimed Sandtoft Old English Pantiles Natural Clay Colour 5 Pack of Sandtoft Old English Pantiles originally a natural clay colour. These tiles have been weathered to a darker colour. These tiles are becoming harder to find. The price is based on £1.20 + vat per tile. These tiles have been made by Goxhill, Sandtoft and Wienerberger and are also known as Arcadia tiles. All tiles are compatible with each other but have different branding.',720,'used',(SELECT "id" FROM "Category" WHERE "slug" = 'roof-tiles-slates' LIMIT 1),'YO32 2RB ',54.0297918,-1.0963469,ARRAY['https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202203/img_1920x_623456220ec249-41214982-41301140.jpeg','https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202203/img_1920x_6234562fbb3984-57290288-34408650.jpeg','https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202203/img_1920x_6234562c9973e0-56071360-53776684.jpeg','https://thereclaimedcompany.com/uploads/images/202203/img_1920x_623456278d3d47-85555013-55915859.jpeg']::text[],'active','sell','PER_UNIT',10,true,24,NULL,true,'2022-03-18T10:01:41Z'::timestamptz,'2022-03-18T10:01:41Z'::timestamptz);

